data.description: Pride of ownership in this amazing two story home located close to shopping and fwy access.  This home features:  4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, laminate flooring through out the home, updated master bathroom with walk in shower, chef kitchen with pull out shelves, granite counters, beautiful cabinets, park like backyard to enjoy a cup on joe in the morning to see the sunrise or evening to see the sunset,  luscious green grass in front and backyard, and much much more.  This amazing home will not last long on the market.
